review_text: Good quality food. Paneer Tikka were nicely done. Paneer Tikka could have been slightly spicier but still good!
Terrible experience! Naan  Lamb Rogan Josh  and Kulfi were all inedible. Naan was completely burnt. Waste of money!
Disappointed with Masala Chai  Chicken Seekh Kebab  Paneer Tikka  Samosa (2 pcs)  and Dal Makhani. Samosa (2 pcs) was cold when it arrived. Not worth the money.
Outstanding experience! The Sweet Lassi and Malai Kofta exceeded all expectations. Sweet Lassi was the star of the meal. Will definitely order again!
Mixed feelings. Palak Paneer  Mango Lassi  Fish Curry  Rasmalai (2 pcs)  and Chicken Seekh Kebab were acceptable. Fish Curry was decent but portion was small for the price.
Not good. Tandoori Roti  Palak Paneer  Dal Makhani  Samosa (2 pcs)  and Chicken Biryani arrived late and cold. Dal Makhani had barely any flavor. Poor quality.
Mixed feelings. Chole Bhature  Paneer Tikka  Dal Makhani  Fish Curry  and Tandoori Roti were acceptable. Chole Bhature was decent but portion was small for the price.
Outstanding experience! The Vegetable Biryani exceeded all expectations. Vegetable Biryani was the star of the meal. Will definitely order again!
Hands down the best Chicken 65 I've ever had! Aloo Tikki Chaat  Samosa (2 pcs)  and Chicken 65 were all prepared beautifully. Fresh and flavorful!
Incredible meal! Rasmalai (2 pcs)  Mango Lassi  Fish Curry  and Butter Chicken arrived hot and fresh. The Butter Chicken was absolutely divine. Highly satisfied!
Hands down the best Aloo Tikki Chaat I've ever had! Masala Chai  Chicken Seekh Kebab  and Aloo Tikki Chaat were all prepared beautifully. Fresh and flavorful!
Perfect in every way! Garlic Naan  Samosa (2 pcs)  Mango Lassi  Chicken Biryani  and Butter Naan were all excellent. Mango Lassi stood out with its rich  authentic taste.
Solid experience. Mango Lassi were well-prepared. Mango Lassi had great flavor. Minor issues with packaging.
Average experience. Malai Kofta  Gajar Halwa  Dal Makhani  and Fish Curry were fine but Dal Makhani was a bit bland. Room for improvement.
Wow! Just wow! Sweet Lassi  Paneer Tikka  Naan  Lamb Rogan Josh  and Tandoori Roti were all fantastic. Sweet Lassi was particularly memorable. Can't wait to order again!
Very satisfied! Dal Makhani were fresh and flavorful. Dal Makhani was the standout dish.
Very satisfied! Paneer Butter Masala were fresh and flavorful. Paneer Butter Masala was the standout dish.
